
# 🏦 Bank Management System

## 🔹 Description
The **Bank Management System** is a **Java-based project** that simulates real-world banking operations.  
It’s perfect for learning **core Java concepts**, **OOP principles**, and basic **database operations**.  

With this system, users can:  
- 📝 Create and manage bank accounts  
- 💰 Deposit and withdraw money  
- 🔄 Transfer funds between accounts  
- 📜 View transaction history  
- 🛠 Perform administrative tasks (if applicable)  

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- **Language:** Java  
- **Framework:** (Add Spring Boot / JDBC / etc. if used)  
- **Database:** MySQL / H2 (choose whichever you used)  
- **IDE:** IntelliJ IDEA / Eclipse  

---

## ✨ Features
- **🧑‍💻 User Registration/Login** – Secure account creation and authentication  
- **📂 Account Management** – View account details and balances  
- **💵 Deposit & Withdrawal** – Perform basic banking operations  
- **💸 Fund Transfer** – Transfer money safely between accounts  
- **📊 Transaction History** – Track all user transactions  
- **🔧 Admin Panel** – Manage users and view system summary (optional)

---

